
The following software is required to build OCaml Reins
  * OCaml versions >= 3.09.2; earlier versions have not been tested.
  * OCaml findlib (http://www.ocaml-programming.de/programming/findlib.html)
  * OMake (http://omake.metaprl.org) version >= 0.9.8.5
  * OUnit (http://www.xs4all.nl/~mmzeeman/ocaml/) version >= 1.0.1.

To build the library simply type:
  $ omake

To install it (using ocaml-findlib) type:
  $ omake install

To build the api documentation type:
  $ omake doc

The documentation can then be installed by copying it from
doc/html/api to the desired location.